data.description: The quintessential Bridger Canyon property, 1859 Bridger Woods is perched above the valley floor and offers incredible views of the surrounding mountain ranges in nearly every direction. Old growth pine groves give way to expansive views of the Bridger Range, the Spanish Peaks, the Tobacco Roots and a spectacular vista of the Bridger Canyon corridor. Situated on nearly 39 acres, the property features a large, lined pond, easy year-round access from a well maintained road and is only 20 minutes to downtown Bozeman and 20 minutes to Bridger Bowl Ski Area. Elk roam the property and the stars light up the night sky - you're a world away but still oh-so-central. Additionally, the property features a large, stately home perched on a premier view site with ample space for family and friends. If you've been searching for the perfect Montana dream property, stop. 1859 Bridger Woods is it.
